n op\u00e9rationnelle du Bund et en 1998 80% (45% en 1994-1998) du capital-actions. En 2004, le journal fut rachet\u00e9 par Espace Media, dont l'actionnaire principal est depuis 2007 la soci\u00e9t\u00e9 Tamedia. Le\u00a0Bund tirait en 2018 \u00e0 37'800\u00a0exemplaires."]], "text_links": [[], [{"start": 470, "end": 497, "mention": "Agence t\u00e9l\u00e9graphique suisse", "href": "/fr/articles/027830/2011-10-27/", "dhsid": "027830", "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q430109", "itemLabel": "Agence t\u00e9l\u00e9graphique suisse", "dhsid": "027830", "namefr": "Agence t\u00e9l\u00e9graphique suisse", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Agence_t%C3%A9l%C3%A9graphique_suisse", "namede": "Keystone-SDA", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keystone-SDA", "nameit": "Agenzia telegrafica svizzera", "articleit": "https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Agenzia_telegrafica_svizzera", "nameen": "Swiss Telegraphic Agency", "articleen": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Swiss_Telegraphic_Agency", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q43229", "instanceofLabel": "organisation", "gndid": "2081619-4"}, {"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q430109", "itemLabel": "Agence t\u00e9l\u00e9graphique suisse", "dhsid": "027830", "namefr": "Agence t\u00e9l\u00e9graphique suisse", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Agence_t%C3%A9l%C3%A9graphique_suisse", "namede": "Keystone-SDA", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keystone-SDA", "nameit": "Agenzia telegrafica svizzera", "articleit": "https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Agenzia_telegrafica_svizzera", "nameen": "Swiss Telegraphic Agency", "articleen": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Swiss_Telegraphic_Agency", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q192283", "instanceofLabel": "agence de presse", "gndid": "2081619-4"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q430109", "wikipedia_page_title": "Agence t\u00e9l\u00e9graphique suisse"}, {"start": 36, "end": 59, "mention": null, "origin"